{"tid":1160951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府應加速市區重建","createTime":"2019-05-18T20:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T17:29:20.000Z","uid":165683,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c274236080f052a3207af95420594291e8026373","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T20:52:24.000Z","msg":"1. 可拆卸危樓<br />\n2. 協助長者生活<br />\n3. 增加土地供應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=jjQR35CjnXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3DjjQR35CjnXw&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=3e7410a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=jjQR35CjnXw</a><br />\n<br />\n政府應可嘗試投資成立新REIT <br />\n以收購舊樓收租<br />\n逐步統一業權<br />\n協助重建 <br />\n<br />\n其次<br />\n應將部分鐵路上蓋公屋同海邊政府用地搬至同區重建地<br />\n並拍賣原有土地<br />\n加快重建速度"},{"pid":"abda67d303d7d32b06bd1d57cbc9653ee051870e","tid":1160951,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T21:24:14.000Z","msg":"市區配套跟唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313a22ca7957cff334a612b2761356c75e73030b","tid":1160951,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"點解要容納新劣質人口？"},{"pid":"dbe33e6b5a38b7eb54d396cab410ae35eebb77d3","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"將黃竹坑警察學院搬去沙頭角或者深圳"},{"pid":"c7fa4ac356d606935bb811756ea040ff012cc65d","tid":1160951,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"應該但政府廢"},{"pid":"bed1efecf58dccf34278c694fd01b5eccd669ffa","tid":1160951,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n狗政府做咁撚多野都係害鳩香港人 做臭香港變腥港<br />\n原來仲有港豬 幻想狗政府 係為民施政<br />\n<br />\n十足十啲賤男中出飛完  個女仔仲死攬住話個男仔好撚愛佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627b516b0d3c8634cc8636f04429864681d71f4a","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbe33e6b5a38b7eb54d396cab410ae35eebb77d3","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"將黃竹坑警察學院搬去沙頭角或者深圳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"黃竹坑警察學院係地鐵站旁痴撚線"},{"pid":"1c8a94650195397f8c1b3dabbf486393fa65d325","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627b516b0d3c8634cc8636f04429864681d71f4a","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbe33e6b5a38b7eb54d396cab410ae35eebb77d3","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"將黃竹坑警察學院搬去沙頭角或者深圳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"黃竹坑警察學院係地鐵站旁痴撚線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"個度夠大起半個太古城"},{"pid":"881d6948357c981d92c1295bebe37155f36ae3cc","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8a94650195397f8c1b3dabbf486393fa65d325","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627b516b0d3c8634cc8636f04429864681d71f4a","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbe33e6b5a38b7eb54d396cab410ae35eebb77d3","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"將黃竹坑警察學院搬去沙頭角或者深圳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"黃竹坑警察學院係地鐵站旁痴撚線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"個度夠大起半個太古城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"而且搬對警察都無壞 可以搬大D 順手更新下"},{"pid":"a18fce9e63af150d7c59a935f0c80fe75b94b8d1","tid":1160951,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbedd27c7192c848ad5ebbb40043dbfeb4e41052","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"樓齡10年持8成業權 可申重建<br />\n<br />\n新加坡私人舊樓樓齡逾10年、業權收集8成以上便符合重建門檻。由於舊樓維修保養成本高，促使當地業主自發收集共識後，向市建局提出重建，模式與本港「市區需求主導計劃」相似，或向私人發展商出售作重建。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡建屋發展局亦會物色樓齡逾20年公營組屋重建，以高地積比率向上發展，並在同區比鄰興建替代組屋，安置或賠償受影響居民。今年初將麥波申巷第81至83座舊組屋分段納入重建計劃，新組屋料2023年完工，重建期5年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2143564/星政府多管齊下加快重建%20港府可仿效規劃\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2143564%2F%E6%98%9F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%A4%9A%E7%AE%A1%E9%BD%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%2520%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%BF%E6%95%88%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=948df5cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2143564/星政府多管齊下加快重建%20港府可仿效規劃</a>"},{"pid":"6c7623552b1435f0581bb0140b8e4dec232eeef2","tid":1160951,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"627b516b0d3c8634cc8636f04429864681d71f4a","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbe33e6b5a38b7eb54d396cab410ae35eebb77d3","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"將黃竹坑警察學院搬去沙頭角或者深圳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"黃竹坑警察學院係地鐵站旁痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"欣澳/人工島整塊地都好"},{"pid":"3df2e386449256c94ead1a4f63dd12cdce0293f8","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZw4m6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZw4m6O.png&h=18de3af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鐡路站旁仲要海邊<br />\n竟然係車廠同物料營運中心...."},{"pid":"58f4d6b2ebc2780cb32aab37ed3ec241eaebe56b","tid":1160951,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"重建左你買得起咩？<br />\n觀塘有辨你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e01c61af82fc7a1ababb836be6bbb71dc2f8806","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"重建浪費金錢時間，又要賠償，又要安置，最壞主意<br />\n<br />\n不所直接發展郊野公園"},{"pid":"7ee64daa5099dd2525b93937505235b98bec758c","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e01c61af82fc7a1ababb836be6bbb71dc2f8806","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"重建浪費金錢時間，又要賠償，又要安置，最壞主意<br />\n<br />\n不所直接發展郊野公園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"不如直接發展郊野公園<br />\n<br />\n真係填海仲有效益過舊區重建"},{"pid":"887acaf0c9092b7809fcc20910a625eb86fad294","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e01c61af82fc7a1ababb836be6bbb71dc2f8806","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"重建浪費金錢時間，又要賠償，又要安置，最壞主意<br />\n<br />\n不所直接發展郊野公園"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"D熔熔爛爛 本身都要維修..."},{"pid":"c1835b411e92818255d3469cb8bc8336c86f6e12","tid":1160951,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"URA 應嘗試將「政府、機構或社區」地帶及「住宅(甲類)」地帶的位置同埋高地價公屋對調。加快重建效率<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據城規會資料，有財團就元朗十八鄉路第13區丈量約份第120約多個地段及毗連政府土地，向該會申請改變土地用途，把當中的「政府、機構或社區」地帶及「住宅(甲類)」地帶的位置對調。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181012/bkn-20181012173035654-1012_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181012%2Fbkn-20181012173035654-1012_00842_001.html&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fsVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=01cf60b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181012/bkn-20181012173035654-1012_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"15a3f48d4443343f1f8c1904d51932ba21f91328","tid":1160951,"uid":9956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"支持姚教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56680a5dfa1846fcba7418d18a9b83067f5d99e7","tid":1160951,"uid":251054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ee64daa5099dd2525b93937505235b98bec758c","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e01c61af82fc7a1ababb836be6bbb71dc2f8806","tid":1160951,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"重建浪費金錢時間，又要賠償，又要安置，最壞主意<br />\n<br />\n不所直接發展郊野公園"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"不如直接發展郊野公園<br />\n<br />\n真係填海仲有效益過舊區重建"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"舊區重建一方面係更新樓宇<br />\n另一方面係擴闊現有既道路<br />\n同埋增加土地可用面積<br />\n亦都可以用現有既交通網絡<br />\n又唔洗起基建<br />\n<br />\n郊野公園範圍係多數根據水塘既引水道黎劃<br />\n唔用水塘填平佢起樓<br />\n<br />\n回歸前填海一般係要等沉降三至五年<br />\n穩定左先可以開始起嘢"},{"pid":"45613adefd316a4e4e91aeb115a850c7cc599001","tid":1160951,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"殺撚哂班150 一係趕撚哂返支那<br />\n大把公屋可以住啦"}]}